high_descs: Walk towards the chair, then hang a left and walk over to the wooden dresser.
Pick up the rightmost book off of the wooden dresser.
Turn around and walk towards the fireplace, then turn left to face the couch.
Put the book on the seat of the couch a ways to the left of the cardboard box.
Turn right and walk over to the left side of the wooden dresser against the wall.
Pick up the book off of the left side of the wooden dresser.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk towards the fireplace, turn left to face the couch.
Put the book on the couch to the left of the book that's already there.
